## States Reference

| State | Meaning | How it is reached |
|-------|---------|-------------------|
| ACTIVE | Process in progress | Organic (on mission creation) or `[[resume X]]` |
| PAUSED | Paused by explicit decision | `[[pause X]]` |
| WAITING | Awaiting external trigger or condition | `[[wait X]]` |
| COMPLETED | Finished (immutable) | `[[complete X]]` |
| EVOLUTION | New SIG derived from a COMPLETED one | Organic (new SIG with Ancestor field) |

### Valid Transitions

```
ACTIVE -----> PAUSED      [[pause X]]
ACTIVE -----> WAITING     [[wait X]]
ACTIVE -----> COMPLETED   [[complete X]]
PAUSED -----> ACTIVE      [[resume X]]
WAITING ----> ACTIVE      [[resume X]]
COMPLETED --> EVOLUTION   (new SIG created with Ancestor reference)
```

> **Key distinction:** PAUSED = explicit decision by the project lead. WAITING = blocked on an external condition.

